quote><br />\n笑死,遲D入面有埋血滴子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依單案出現過幾多次電腦線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n乜唔係見條屍個刻知用咩上吊咩 點會疑使用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所有野都要交比法庭審判<br />\n例如傷人案，1打1<br />\n佢都會話，有人攻擊另一人<br />\n唔會話疑犯<br />\n<br />\n即係事件敍述+嫌疑人<br />\n一定要呢個format"},{"pid":"92555942e70caee8b95e1d798a571224ee8908f9","tid":238524,"uid":21260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T08:14:19.000Z","msg":"個女仔洗唔洗認屍<br />\n咁咪知係畏罪定被自殺"},{"pid":"9760c723e2df2feeee26f1e518fe7e90376dd06b","tid":238524,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T08:27:29.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"ef58c803af920a9403607f97f78bd2ab9c6f4a41","tid":238524,"uid":15205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T08:31:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個女仔洗唔洗認屍<br />\n咁咪知係畏罪定被自殺</blockquote><br />\n條友受過咁多次實有相 , 唔洗去認屍既"},{"pid":"c2101a4e069088e430c858d743000d5a5a480c9f","tid":238524,"uid":63078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T08:33:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>案件已交由東九龍總區重案組調查，仍在調查疑犯自縊原因，以及事發時羈留室內情況，以及為何疑犯身上有Lan線。據悉，疑犯犯案時曾與女受害人聊天，之後再將對方強姦，事後再與女受害人聊天才離開。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/90216?utm_content=buffer4d918&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F90216%3Futm_content%3Dbuffer4d918%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=bcb43c72\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/90216?utm_content=buffer4d918&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a><br />\nLan線？</blockquote><br />\n點解會事前事後都有傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8